2026-05-13T16:27:10.2176566Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-13T16:27:10.2177807Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-13T16:27:10.2178996Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
